Carl Ph. SCHWALB v. L. B. BROMFIELD, as Receiver of the Globe National Bank of Denver. No. 35. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. June 8, 1929. Wilbur E. Denious and Hudson Moore, both of Denver, Colo., for appellant. Ralph Hartzell, of Denver, .Colo., for appellee.

Before LEWIS, Circuit Judge, and SYMES, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed June 8, 1929, per stipulation.
